the number of commits, number of branches, things like that, that indicate that a study

00:12:48.940 --> 00:12:52.859
is struggling. And you can actually proactively reach them and say, hey, do you need some

00:12:52.859 --> 00:12:57.900
help? They're very appreciative of that. So that's something that I think is very cool,

00:12:57.900 --> 00:13:03.340
something that I'm very proud of. The other thing is the tool catalog. One other question

00:13:03.340 --> 00:13:08.539
a VP is going to ask you is going to be a question around finance. Return on investment.

